As a Tenant (Property Owner)
Register as a Tenant when creating your account

Create a listing by clicking "Add Listing" in the navigation bar

Fill in property details:

Title and description

Property type (Boarding House, Apartment, etc.)

Location (Cebu City or Lapu-Lapu City)

Price per night

Maximum occupants

Amenities (comma-separated)

Upload up to 3 images

Manage your listings from "My Listings" page (Edit/Delete)

Respond to booking requests from the "Bookings" page

Reply to buyer messages from the "Messages" page

As a Buyer (Renter)
Register as a Buyer when creating your account

Browse listings from the "Listings" page

Filter results by:

Location

Property type

Price range

Number of occupants

View on map by clicking the "Map View" tab

Book a room by clicking "Book This Room" on any listing

Message the tenant using the messaging section on the listing page

Track your bookings from the "Bookings" page

Cancel pending bookings if needed

As Admin
Go to /admin and log in with superuser credentials

Manage all users, listings, bookings, and messages

Approve or remove content as needed
